Now that you know I know alot more about these 2 classes than 99.99% of the people in EQ will ever know.  I even had the FIRST Druid Website... Pepto's Playland... was put up day 1 of release (Was illegal to put up before then) and taken down 2 mths later when Twilight put up EQ druids.  I e-mailed him told him to take anything he needed I was bringing mine down.... 'course he had most of the same info at that point.<br>
