<br>
I park my damn bard and play mana song... then I either quad kite shissar Revnents in the Grey or Root/DoT crap... That is the easiest way to kill stuff 2 boxing with a bard.<br>
<br>
If bards were lazy and had it easy.. don't you think my bard would play a more active role in the killing?<br>
<br>
To be able to melee stuff I have to 3 box my shaman so I can slow the mobs.<br>
